House Resolution 727
By: Representative Williams of the 148th
A RESOLUTION
1 Commending the Wilcox County Lady Patriots Basketball Team for winning the 2025
2 GHSA Class A Division II Girls Basketball State Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Wilcox County girls basketball team has established and maintained a proud
4 tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, this superlative team has completed another triumphant season of basketball
6 competition by posting an outstanding record of 28 wins and one loss; and
7 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
8 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
9 2025 campaign, the team captured its first girls basketball state championship in school
10 history; and
11 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
12 athletic ability, the dedication and hard work, and the unity of purpose and spirit of each
13 member of the team; its superb offensive and defensive talents; and the astute direction of
14 Head Coach Santita Coon; and
